manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "auth-service"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/api/main.rs"
name = "api"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[package]
name = "auth-service"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
axum = "0.7.4"
reqwest = "0.11.26"
serde_json = "1.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.36"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.5.0"
features = ["fs"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.7.0"
features = ["v4", "serde"]

[dev-dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.26"
features = ["json"]
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.32.0"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "auth_service"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
